flowchart TD
    %% title: Chapter 8: Visibility and Access Control Flow
    
    Start([Define Item]) --> Visibility{Visibility?}
    
    Visibility -->|private| PrivateScope[Default - private]
    Visibility -->|pub| PubScope[Public]
    Visibility -->|"pub(crate)"| CrateScope["pub(crate)"]
    Visibility -->|"pub(super)"| SuperScope["pub(super)"]
    Visibility -->|"pub(in path)"| InScope["pub(in path)"]
    
    PrivateScope --> PrivateCheck{Access from?}
    PrivateCheck -->|same module| Allow1[✅ Allow]
    PrivateCheck -->|child module| Allow2[✅ Allow]
    PrivateCheck -->|external| Deny1[❌ Deny]
    
    PubScope --> PubCheck{Access from?}
    PubCheck -->|anywhere| Allow3[✅ Allow]
    
    CrateScope --> CrateCheck{Access from?}
    CrateCheck -->|same crate| Allow4[✅ Allow]
    CrateCheck -->|external crate| Deny2[❌ Deny]
    
    SuperScope --> SuperCheck{Access from?}
    SuperCheck -->|parent module| Allow5[✅ Allow]
    SuperCheck -->|sibling module| Allow6[✅ Allow via parent]
    SuperCheck -->|external| Deny3[❌ Deny]
    
    InScope --> InCheck{Access from?}
    InCheck -->|in specified path| Allow7[✅ Allow]
    InCheck -->|outside path| Deny4[❌ Deny]
    
    Allow1 --> End([End])
    Allow2 --> End
    Deny1 --> End
    Allow3 --> End
    Allow4 --> End
    Deny2 --> End
    Allow5 --> End
    Allow6 --> End
    Deny3 --> End
    Allow7 --> End
    Deny4 --> End
    
    style Start fill:#b2f2bb
    style End fill:#b2f2bb
    style Visibility fill:#fef3c7
    style PrivateCheck fill:#fef3c7
    style PubCheck fill:#fef3c7
    style CrateCheck fill:#fef3c7
    style SuperCheck fill:#fef3c7
    style InCheck fill:#fef3c7
    
    style Allow1 fill:#b2f2bb
    style Allow2 fill:#b2f2bb
    style Allow3 fill:#b2f2bb
    style Allow4 fill:#b2f2bb
    style Allow5 fill:#b2f2bb
    style Allow6 fill:#b2f2bb
    style Allow7 fill:#b2f2bb
    
    style Deny1 fill:#ffc9c9
    style Deny2 fill:#ffc9c9
    style Deny3 fill:#ffc9c9
    style Deny4 fill:#ffc9c9
